Looks like other packages in contrib/ are available in Windows except tfprof.
It seems it's because this comment
"add_python_module("tensorflow/contrib/tfprof" DONTCOPY) # SWIG wrapper not implemented."

I'm trying to enable tfprof in Windows and see what error presubmit will give me.

body:
Looks like other packages in contrib/ are available in Windows except tfprof.
It seems it's because this comment
"add_python_module("tensorflow/contrib/tfprof" DONTCOPY)  # SWIG wrapper not implemented."

I'm trying to enable tfprof in Windows and see what error presubmit will give me.
